Hey everyone! 👋

For your assignment,  we want you to build a To-Do List app using HTML, CSS and JS!

It should have:
- An input box + button to add tasks
- A delete button on each task
- make use of different tags to show what the app is meant for ( information)
- include you name and a small bio 
- add an avatar 

That's it — keep it simple, make it yours. Change the colors, the font, the vibe. We don't want 20 identical grey boxes 😄

No libraries, no frameworks — pure HTML, CSS and JS only. If you can build this you genuinely understand everything we covered today 🙌

Any difficulty you face or any help you need, pls reach out to mentor! Happy to help 🤗

